nces%20in%20our%20country.%20I've%20had%20so%20much%20experience%20over%20the%20years%20of%20watching%20people%20who%20struggle%20to%20get%20what%20people%20would%20define%20as%20a%20second%20chance%20when%20I%20realized%20they%20never%20really%20had%20a%20first%20chance%20investment%3A%20no%20pre-K%20education%2C%20mothers%20who%20were%20delivering%20babies%20without%20maternal%20and%20prenatal%20care%2C%20the%20people%20who%20never%20really%20got%20that%20economic%20opportunity%2C%20and%20people%20who%20haven't%20had%20access%20to%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomebody%20has%20to%20fight%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20people%20whose%20voices%20are%20not%20heard%20and%20whose%20lived%20experiences%20are%20not%20understood%20truly%20have%20what%20they%20need%20to%20be%20successful%20in%20our%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226308%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Angela%20Alsobrooks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c00b4b6fcb546d2d4bf1ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224205%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlsobrooks%20served%20as%20the%20Prince%20George's%20County%20state's%20attorney%20from%202011%20to%202018.%3Cp%3ETom%20Williams%2FCQ-Roll%20Call%2C%20Inc%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJD%3A%20You%20spoke%20about%20the%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20humans%20in%20order%20to%20fully%20address%20economic%20issues.%20As%20a%20public%20official%2C%20what%20have%20you%20seen%20that's%20driven%20your%20worldview%20on%20this%20issue%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAA%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESomething%20as%20instrumental%20as%20having%20childcare%20is%20really%20important.%20I%20was%20a%20prosecutor%20for%20many%20years%20and%20had%20a%20number%20of%20cases%20that%20happened%20almost%20in%20the%20same%20timespan%20where%20there%20were%20small%20children%20who%20had%20been%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20cases%20in%20particular%20was%20the%20case%20of%20a%20young%20boy%20who%20was%202%20years%20old.%20His%20mother%20went%20to%20work%20and%20she%20left%20the%20child%20at%20home%20with%20someone%20because%20she%20couldn't%20afford%20childcare%2C%20and%20that%20person%20murdered%20her%20child.%20Rather%20than%20looking%20at%20her%20and%20asking%20what%20was%20wrong%20with%20her%20because%20she%20left%20her%20child%20in%20the%20care%20of%20a%20person%20who%20was%20unsafe%2C%20I%20realized%20immediately%20as%20a%20mother%20myself%20with%20a%20young%20child%20of%20how%20cost%20prohibitive%20childcare%20is.%20I%20was%20working%20as%20a%20lawyer%2C%20so%20I%20know%20a%20person%20who%20had%20a%20different%20salary%20would%20have%20difficulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Flocal%2Fpublic-safety%2Fdo-you-know-whos-watching-your-children%2F2016%2F04%2F14%2F552e9c98-025d-11e6-9203-7b8670959b88_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20to%20make%20sure%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20we%20made%20available%20to%20young%20families%20the%20ability%20to%20put%20in%20their%20zip%20code%20and%20put%20in%20their%20salary%20and%20find%20licensed%20childcare%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20where%20they%20live.%20We%20have%20to%20make%20those%20kinds%20of%20resources%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmgaleg.maryland.gov%2Fcmte_testimony%2F2021%2Fehe%2F1BLLgtT3wym4fVCY4GFm-rEpnkog_ARAX.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavailable%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20people%20in%20office%20who%20are%20sensitive%20to%20the%20challenges%20and%20needs%20of%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJD%3A%20In%20what%20other%20ways%20would%20you%20say%20your%20time%20as%20state's%20attorney%20prepared%20you%20for%20the%20Senate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20best%20preparation%20ever%20because%20I%20got%20to%20sit%20close%20to%20families.%20I%20spent%2013%20years%20inside%20a%20courthouse%20and%20inside%20a%20courtroom.%20I%20saw%20what%20happened%20when%20there%20was%20no%20mental%20health%20care%2C%20when%20there%20was%20no%20care%20for%20people%20who%20had%20addictions%2C%20what%20the%20dearth%20of%20affordable%20housing%20meant%20to%20families%2C%20and%20what%20it%20meant%20for%20parents%20to%20have%20higher%20incomes%20so%20they%20could%20sit%20down%20and%20do%20homework%20with%20their%20kids%20at%20the%20table%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20county%20executive%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fdc-md-va%2F2022%2F05%2F11%2Fprince-georges-medstar-mental-health-alsobrooks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopened%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20mental%20health%20and%20addiction%20care%20facility%20in%20the%20county.%20This%20was%20in%20response%20to%20what%20I%20saw%20when%20I%20realized%20that%2070%25%20of%20the%20people%20we%20arrested%20every%20day%20and%20took%20to%20the%20local%20departments%20of%20corrections%20were%20intoxicated%20when%20they%20arrived%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20third%20of%20the%20people%20we%20arrested%20were%20on%20psychotropic%20medications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJD%3A%20What%20do%20you%20think%20the%20Senate%20isn't%20doing%20that%20they%20should%20be%20prioritizing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAA%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20issues%20that%20are%20at%20the%20kitchen%20tables%20of%20everyday%2C%20hardworking%20families.%20And%20I%20don't%20know%20that%20they%20are.%20If%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftuberville-finally-caves-lifts-hold-on-most-military-promotions-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocus%20on%20blocking%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20as%20Senator%20%5BTommy%5D%20Tuberville%20did%20%E2%80%94%20over%20400%20military%20appointments%20at%20a%20time%20when%20our%20country's%20safety%20and%20security%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20it%20tells%20me%20that%20we're%20out%20of%20sync%20in%20so%20many%20ways.%20The%20Senate%20isn't%20representative%20of%20the%20lived%