jriwal%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20his%20role%20in%20an%20alleged%20excise%20policy%20scam%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fkejriwal-issued-ed-summons-for-fifth-time-in-delhi-excise-policy-case%2Farticle67798120.ece%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20fifth%20time%20on%20January%2031%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20skipped%20this%20summons%20as%20he%20did%20the%20previous%20four%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20claimed%20that%20Kejriwal%20%E2%80%9Cintentionally%20disobeyed%E2%80%9D%20every%20summons%20it%20had%20issued%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmaking%20each%20of%20such%20omission%20or%20disobedience%20a%20separate%20offence%E2%80%9D%2C%20PTI%20quoted%20its%20complaint%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20chief%20metropolitan%20magistrate%20Divya%20Malhotra%20said%20that%20Kejriwal%20was%20%E2%80%9Clegally%20bound%E2%80%9D%20to%20attend%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20summons%20in%20person%20and%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cpurportedly%20failed%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20complaint%20and%20the%20material%20placed%20on%20record%2C%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%20offence%20under%20Section%20174%20of%20the%20IPC%20is%20made%20out%E2%80%9D%20against%20Kejriwal%2C%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20law%20dealing%20with%20the%20disobedience%20of%20an%20order%20given%20by%20a%20public%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20asked%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20court%20on%20February%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20complaint%2C%20the%20ED%20added%20that%20Kejriwal%20%E2%80%9Cis%20a%20high-ranking%20public%20functionary%20who%20is%20expected%20to%20obey%20the%20law.%20If%20such%20persons%20holding%20such%20high%20officers%20disobey%20the%20law%2C%20then%20it%20will%20set%20a%20wrong%20example%20for%20the%20common%20man%20i.e.%20the%20%3Cem%3Eaam%20aadmi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20also%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20