20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20part%2C%20Lyft's%20earnings%20guarantee%20is%20a%20response%20to%20drivers'%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20take%20driving%20as%20seriously%20as%20drivers%20do.%20That's%20why%20we%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20listening%20to%20drivers%20and%20getting%20behind%20the%20wheel%20ourselves%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Risher%2C%20Lyft%20CEO%2C%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20heard%20lots%20of%20feedback%20around%20consistent%20themes%20%E2%80%94%20earnings%2C%20deactivations%2C%20and%20safety%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we're%20taking%20action%20to%20address%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyft%20also%20noted%20that%20drivers%20can%20now%20see%20the%20breakdown%20of%20how%20each%20rider's%20payments%20are%20split%20between%20drivers%2C%20Lyft%2C%20and%20external%20fees.%20Drivers%20will%20also%20see%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20every%20cent%20of%20the%20rider%20fare%20goes%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20new%20earnings%20summary%20in%20the%20Lyft%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20ride-hailing%20drivers%20are%20skeptical%20about%20how%20much%20Lyft's%20policy%20changes%20will%20benefit%20drivers.%20Sergio%20Avedian%2C%20an%20Uber%20driver%20who%20is%20a%20senior%20contributor%20to%20the%20gig-driver-advocacy%20blog%20and%20YouTube%20channel%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherideshareguy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Rideshare%20Guy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20up%20to%20a%20quarter%20of%20rider%20payments%20could%20continue%20to%20go%20to%20external%20fees%20%E2%80%94%20so%20drivers%20may%20only%20be%20guaranteed%2070%25%20of%20a%20reduced%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvedian%20acknowledged%20that%20Lyft's%20change%20would%20benefit%20the%2015%25%20of%20drivers%20who%20earned%20less%20than%2070%25%20of%20rider%20payments%20after%20external%20fees.%20But%20he%20said%20he's%20not%20confident%20that%20the%20typical%20driver%2C%20who%20Lyft%20said%20is%20earni