.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20always%20wanted%20to%20own%20a%20home.%20It%20was%20pretty%20evident%20that%20we'd%20have%20to%20work%20for%20many%20years%20before%20we'd%20be%20able%20to%20purchase%20one%20in%20California%2C%26quot%3B%20Lagos%20told%20BI%20in%20December.%20%26quot%3BThe%20opportunities%20were%20much%20greater%20for%20us%20in%20Texas%20than%20they%20were%20in%20California.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20person%20of%20color%20who%20recently%20moved%20to%20%E2%80%94%20or%20moved%20out%20of%20%E2%80%94%20Texas%2C%20and%20wants%20to%20share%20your%20story%3F%20Email%20reporter%20Alcynna%20Lloyd%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aalloyd%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ealloyd%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-of-color-texas-population-growth-economy-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707330446000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd2dfa7a3d2714887736d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-of-color-texas-population-growth-economy-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jobs%2C%20relatively%20affordable%20homes%2C%20and%20a%20cheaper%20cost%20of%20living%20are%20luring%20young%20people%20of%20color%20to%20Texas%2C%20where%20the%20population%20is%20surging%20and%20the%20economy%20is%20taking%20off.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22alloyd%40insider.com%20(Alcynna%20Lloyd%2CYoonji%20Han%2CNoah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-of-color-texas-population-growth-economy-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pennsylvania%20wants%20student-loan%20borrowers%20in%20the%20state%20to%20take%20on%20less%20debt.%20Here's%20how.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pennsylvania%20Gov.%20Josh%20Shapiro%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a2777a3d271488787f77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221998%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGovernor%20of%20Pennsylvania%20Josh%20Shapiro%20.%3Cp%3EGilbert%20Carrasquillo%2FGC%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPennsylvania%20Gov.%20Josh%20Shapiro%20unveiled%20a%20plan%20to%20overhaul%20higher%20education%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20proposed%20reducing%20tuition%20to%20%241%2C000%20for%20families%20earning%20below%20%2470%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20would%20also%20increase%20state%20grants%20for%20students%20by%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPennsylvania's%20governor%20has%20a%20plan%20to%20make%20higher%20education%20more%20affordable%20%E2%80%94%20and%20prevent%20the%20state's%20residents%20from%20taking%20on%20unaffordable%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Pennsylvania%20Gov.%20Josh%20Shapiro%20unveiled%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.governor.pa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fgovernor-shapiro-unveils-2024-25-budget-proposal-to-get-stuff-done-create-opportunity-and-advance-real-freedom-for-all-pennsylvanians%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebudget%20request%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202024-2025%2C%20which%20proposed%20increased%20funding%20for%20K-12%20education%2C%20small%20businesses%2C%20public%20transportation%2C%20and%20childcare%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20Along%20with%20proposals%20for%20those%20continued%20investments%2C%20Shapiro%20also%20put%20forth%20a%20%24975%20million%20proposal%20to%20overhaul%20the%20higher%20education%20system%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.governor.pa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fgovernor-shapiro-delivers-new-blueprint-for-higher-education-focused-on-competitiveness-and-workforce-development-grounded-in-access-and-affordability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFirst%20unveiled%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20end%20of%20January%2C%20Shapiro's%20plan%20for%20higher%20education%20would%20unite%20Pennsylvania's%2010%20state-owned%20universities%20with%20its%2015%20community%20colleges%20under%20a%20single%20system%20that%20would%20ensure%20families%20earning%20up%20to%20%2470%2C000%20a%20year%20will%20pay%20no%20more%20than%20%241%2C000%20in%20tuition%20and%20fees%20per%20semester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20would%20also%20increase%20state%20grants%20by%20%241%2C000%2C%20bringing%20the%20maximum%20award%20to%20%246%2C750%20beginning%20in%20fiscal%20year%202025.%20And%2C%20according%20to%20the%20budget%20request%2C%20the%20state%20proposed%20investing%20%24279%20million%20annually%20beginning%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202025%20%26quot%3Bso%20Pennsylvania%20students%20can%20attend%20college%20in-state%20with%20a%20limited%20debt%20load%20after%20they%20graduate%20and%20can%20enter%20the%20workforce%20ready%20to%20start%20their%20careers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20time%20to%20build%20on%20this%20new%20blueprint%20for%20higher%20education%20in%20Pennsylvania%20and%20leave%20a%20lasting%20legacy%20on%20this%20Commonwealth%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20said%20during%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.governor.pa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fgovernor-shapiros-2024-25-budget-address-as-prepared%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebudget%20address%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20if%20we%20can%20ensure%20that%20Pennsylvanians%20receive%20a%20great%20education%2C%20from%20Pre-K%20through%20an%20apprenticeship%20program%20all%20the%20way%20to%20college%20graduation%2C%20if%20we%20can%20give%20Pennsylvanians%20the%20freedom%20to%20chart%20their%20own%20course%20and%20the%20opportunity%20to%20succeed%2C%20then%20economic%20opportunity%20will%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Shapiro%20said%20his%20plan%20to%20overhaul%20the%20higher%20education%20system%20would%20bring%20the%20state%20from%2049th%20in%20the%20nation%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20state%20investment%20to%2022nd%2C%20it's%20unclear%20at%20this%20point%20if%20the%20state's%20legislature%20will%20approve%20his%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20of%20the%20leaders%20at%20local%20universities%20have%20expressed%20support%20for%20the%20plan.%20Joan%20Gabel%2C%20chancellor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pittsburgh%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.governor.pa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fgovernor-shapiro-delivers-new-blueprint-for-higher-education-focused-on-competitiveness-and-workforce-development-grounded-in-access-and-affordability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20she's%20pleased%20that%20Shapiro's%20plan%20will%20%26quot%3Bgive%20Pennsylvania%20students%20greater%20opportunities%20for%20affordable%2C%20high-quality%20higher%20education%20and%20to%20bolster%20the%20role%20of%20colleges%20and%20universities%20like%20Pitt%20in%20driving%20Pennsylvania's%20economic%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20states%20are%20taking%20similar%20approaches%20to%20address%20higher%20education%20affordability.%20Colorado%20Gov.%20Jared%20Polis%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcoloradonewsline.com%2Fbriefs%2Fgov-polis-pushes-for-more-apprenticeship-programs-in-colorado-state-agencies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epushed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20fall%20to%20expand%20apprenticeship%20opportunities%20in%20the%20state%20to%20allow%20residents%20to%20attain%20employment%20without%20dealing%20with%20the%20costs%20of%20a%20four-year%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20reform%20is%20happening%20at%20the%20federal%20level%2C%20as%20well.%20Since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-issues-debt-relief-broken-industry-2023-9%5C%22%20targ