%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-apple-vision-pro-looks-like-inside-teardown-video-2024-2%5C%22%3EApple's%20new%20headset%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20impressed%20by%20our%20experience%20with%20the%20device%20thus%20far%2C%20and%20believe%20that%20consuming%20content%20-%20immersive%20video%2C%20mixed%20reality%20gaming%2C%20live%20sports%2C%20etc.%20-%20will%20be%20the%20initial%20consumer%20'killer%20app'%20on%20the%20device%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Morgan%20Stanley%20team%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20bank's%20Fall%202023%20AlphaWise%20Smartphone%20survey%2C%2033%25%20of%20US%20iPhone%20users%20said%20they%20would%20likely%20purchase%20the%20product%20within%20the%20first%2012%20months%20of%20its%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20forecasts%20that%20Apple%20can%20ramp%20up%20its%20revenue%20from%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20to%20%244%20billion%20within%20four%20years%2C%20which%20would%20rank%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20launch%20for%20AirPods%2C%20and%20behind%20that%20of%20the%20Apple%20Watch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221212%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple%20Vision%20Pro%20revenue%20outlook%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3ba786fcb546d2d4d0b53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22909%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20expects%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20to%20underperform%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20over%20the%20next%20several%20years.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BW%5De%20believe%20that%20until%20Apple%20introduces%20new%20form%20factors%20at%20more%20attainable%20price%20points%2C%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20will%20remain%20a%20niche%20consumer%20device%20unlikely%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20impact%20in%20the%20Apple%20financial%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ELong-term%20upside%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20Apple's%20track%20record%20with%20the%20iPhone%20and%20other%20products%2C%20the%20successive%20generations%20of%20the%20Apple%20Vision%20Pro%20should%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20view%2C%20this%20promising%20trajectory%20is%20%26quot%3Beffectively%20a%20free%20call%20option%26quot%3B%20on%20Apple%20innovation%2C%20and%20it%20could%20continue%20to%20bring%20fresh%20upside%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20experience%20of%20picking%20up%20the%20product%20at%20an%20Apple%20store%2C%20for%20starters%2C%20is%20well-scripted%20and%20extremely%20useful%2C%20the%20analysts%20said.%20The%2030-minute%20demo%20is%20unlike%20any%20other%2C%20and%20it's%20useful%20for%20consumers%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20control%20the%20headset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20content%20consumption%20available%20on%20the%20twin%2C%20high-definition%20screens%20is%20%26quot%3Bincredible%2C%26quot%3B%20Woodring%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20entirely%20new%20way%20of%20consuming%20content%2C%20and%20is%20as%20close%20to%20the%20'real%20world'%20as%20you%20can%20get%20without%20physically%20being%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20we%20were%20-%20by%20far%20-%20most%20impressed%20with%20the%20device...the%20Vision%20Pro%20is%20clearly%20constructed%20to%20become%20a%20content%20powerhouse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20eye-tracking%20feature%20and%20external%20cameras%20are%20more%20accurate%20and%20responsive%20than%20expected%2C%20and%20Morgan%20Stanley%20said%20it%20could%20soon%20become%20a%20helpful%20productivity%20tool%20similar%20to%20a%20computer%20with%20multiple%20displays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20product%20could%20take%20some%20getting%20used%20to%2C%20as%20far%20as%20the%20comfortability%20of%20placing%20a%20small%20computer%20on%20your%20face.%20The%20analysts%20said%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20they%20would%20still%20opt%20to%20watch%20a%20movie%20on%20a%20regular%20TV%20screen%20rather%20than%20the%20Vision%20Pro%2C%20even%20though%20the%20latter%20would%20be%20more%20immersive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20areas%20for%20improvement%2C%20the%20analysts%20pointed%20to%20the%20native%20app%20ecosystem%20still%20needing%20to%20be%20built%20out%2C%20better%20video%20pixelation%20around%20the%20periphery%20of%20the%20displays%2C%20and%20a%20lower%20price%20point%20to%20allow%20for%20more%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20stock%20hovered%20at%20%24189%20a%20share%20after%20midday%20on%20Wednesday.%20Morgan%20Stanley%20maintained%20its%2012-month%20price%20target%20of%20%24220%2C%20representing%20potential%20upside%20of%20about%2016%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-vision-pro-aapl-stock-price-morgan-stanley-tech-stocks-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707329453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3b5857a3d2714887890fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fapple-vision-pro-aapl-stock-price-morgan-stanley-tech-stocks-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Morgan%20Stanley%20noted%20Wall%20Street's%20muted%20reaction%20so%20far%20despite%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20representing%20a%20%26quot%3Bfree%20call%20option%26quot%3B%20on%20Apple%20innovation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22prosen%40insider.com%20(Phil%20Rosen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fapple-vision-pro-aapl-stock-price-morgan-stanley-tech-stocks-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fighter%20box%20office%20collection%20day%2014%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707329324000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107502649%2Cimgsize-53756.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.c