%20carried%20out%20fewer%20attacks%20but%20garnered%20larger%20payments%20per%20attack%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20%26quot%3Bransomware%20as%20a%20service%26quot%3B%20has%20also%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20attacks.%20Using%20the%20model%2C%20outsiders%20can%20use%20a%20ransomware%20program%20and%20then%20pay%20its%20creator%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20proceeds%20from%20the%20hack.%20These%20methods%20require%20much%20less%20technical%20know-how%20on%20the%20part%20of%20criminals%20in%20order%20to%20carry%20out%2C%20Chainalysis%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChainalysis%20reported%20previously%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fnorth-korean-crypto-hacker-defi-finance-security-cyber-crime-lazarus-2024-1%3F_gl%3D1*fxfjf2*_ga*ODAxNTgzMjcxLjE3MDU5NTE2MDY.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTcwNzMxNzEyOS44My4wLjE3MDczMTcxMzAuNTkuMC4w%5C%22%3ENorth%20Korean-linked%3C%2Fa%3E%20hacks%20of%20cryptocurrency%20platforms%20reached%20a%20record%20high%20in%202023%2C%20though%20the%20year%20also%20saw%20a%2041%25%20decrease%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20crypto%20stolen%20by%20these%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-cyber-crimes-ransom-payments-record-hacks-ransomware-2023-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707328038000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3ab8e43bb77284ba46fad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fcrypto-cyber-crimes-ransom-payments-record-hacks-ransomware-2023-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rise%20of%20%26quot%3Bransomware%20as%20a%20service%26quot%3B%20means%20less%20tech%20skill%20is%20required%20to%20carry%20out%20an%20attack%2C%20Chainalysis%20said%20in%20a%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22yzhan%40insider.com%20(Yuheng%20Zhan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A