0be%20willing%20to%20pay%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%20price%20has%20been%20set%20yet%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F02%2F06%2Fespn-fox-and-warner-bros-discovery-to-launch-joint-sports-streaming-platform-this-year.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20%2450%20a%20month%20could%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Blogical%20starting%20point%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20service%2C%20citing%20a%20source%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20That'd%20compare%20to%20the%20roughly%20%2470%20a%20month%20YouTube%20TV%20charges%20for%20about%20100%20live%20channels%20including%20major%20sports%20networks%20and%20some%20locals%20depending%20on%20the%20market.%20But%2C%20keep%20in%20mind%2C%20while%20the%20new%20sports%20streamer%20will%20have%20most%20sports%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20one-stop%20shop.%20Games%20on%20NBC%20and%20Paramount's%20channels%20and%20streamers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20some%20NFL%20matchups%20and%20leagues%20like%20the%20English%20Premier%20League%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20missing%2C%20as%20will%20the%20local%20channels%20where%20viewers%20watch%20their%20regional%20teams%20outside%20the%20national%20broadcasts.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%2C%20media%20conglomerates%20have%20had%20a%20rough%20time%20making%20the%20streaming%20model%20work%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20exorbitantly%20priced%20sports%20properties%20Disney%2C%20Fox%2C%20and%20WBD%20plan%20to%20carry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Verna%20at%20Insider%20Intelligence%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20Business%20Insider's%20parent%20company.%20%26quot%3BJoining%20forces%20might%20give%20them%20scale%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20solve%20the%20riddle%20of%20how%20to%20monetize%20this%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20the%20cable%20companies%20react%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20new%20streamer%20could%20be%20the%20thing%20that%20finally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fespn-wbd-new-sports-streaming-service-could-kill-cable-tv-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekills%20cable%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Are%20the%20cable%20giants%20ready%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20that%20business%3F%20And%20are%20ESPN%20et%20al%20really%20ready%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20the%20high-margin%2C%20albeit%20shrinking%20revenue%20they%20get%20from%20the%20cable%20carriage%20fees%3F%20Some%20cable%20operators%2C%20including%20Charter%2C%20have%20indicated%20they're%20willing%20to%20move%20on%20as%20they%20focus%20on%20their%20more%20profitable%20internet%20businesses%2C%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbusiness-news%2Fdisney-vs-charter-spectrum-explained-1235581770%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshifting%20subscribers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20virtual%20pay-TV%20services%20like%20YouTube%20TV.%20If%20the%20cable%20companies%20get%20on%20board%2C%20the%20programmers%20could%20enlist%20them%20to%20shift%20subscribers%20to%20their%20new%20sports%20streamer.%20Or%20the%20operators%20could%20balk%20at%20an%20open%20attack%20on%20their%20legacy%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20would%20this%20joint%20venture%20be%20any%20better%20than%20Hulu's%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHulu%20launched%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20Netflix%20did%20in%20streaming%20but%20fell%20behind%20in%20part%20because%20of%20its%20ownership%20structure%2C%20which%20was%20initially%20a%20JV%20between%20Disney%2C%20Fox's%20former%20owner%2C%20and%20NBC.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20it%20was%20a%20JV%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20for%20Hulu%20to%20maximize%20the%20opportunity%20in%20front%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20Weiser%20wrote%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmadisonandwallsubscription.substack.com%2Fp%2Fclownco-20-hulu-for-sports-announced%3Futm_source%3Dpost-email-title%26publication_id%3D2209131%26post_id%3D141446871%26utm_campaign%3Demail-post-title%26isFreemail%3Dtrue%26r%3D1iid5%26utm_medium%3Demail%