ontent%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20International%20human%20rights%20organisation%20Amnesty%20International%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20cessation%20of%20the%20widespread%20and%20unlawful%20demolitions%20of%20Muslims%E2%80%99%20homes%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20places%20of%20worship%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20released%20two%20reports%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%207)%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20speak%20up%2C%20your%20house%20will%20be%20demolished%E2%80%99%3A%20Bulldozer%20Injustice%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Unearthing%20Accountability%3A%20JCB%E2%80%99s%20Role%20and%20Responsibility%20in%20Bulldozer%20Injustice%20in%20India%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20document%20the%20punitive%20demolition%20of%20Muslim%20properties%20in%20at%20least%20five%20states%20using%20JCB-branded%20bulldozers%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20hate%20campaign%20against%20the%20minority%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgn%C3%A8s%20Callamard%2C%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Secretary%20General%20expressed%20deep%20concern%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20unlawful%20demolition%20of%20Muslim%20properties%20by%20the%20Indian%20authorities%2C%20peddled%20as%20%E2%80%98bulldozer%20justice%2C%E2%80%99%20is%20cruel%20and%20appalling.%20Such%20displacement%20and%20dispossession%20are%20deeply%20unjust%2C%20unlawful%2C%20and%20discriminatory.%20They%20are%20destroying%20families%20and%20must%20stop%20immediately.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20halt%20the%20de%20facto%20policy%20of%20demolishing%20people%E2%80%99s%20homes%20as%20a%20form%20of%20extra-judicial%20punishment%20and%20ensure%20nobody%20is%20made%20homeless%20as%20a%20result%20of%20forced%20evictions%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20press%20note%2C%20adding%20that%20adequate%20compensation%20is%20given%20to%20all%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20demolitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-unconstitutionality-of-bulldozer-justice%5C%22%3EThe%20Unconstitutionality%20of%20%E2%80%98Bulldozer%20Justice%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20investigations%2C%20between%20April%20and%20June%202022%2C%20authorities%20in%20five%20states%20carried%20out%20demolitions%20as%20a%20form%20of%20%E2%80%98punishment%E2%80%99%20following%20communal%20violence%20or%20protests%20against%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20detail%20128%20documented%20demolitions%2C%20with%20at%20least%2033%20instances%20of%20JCB%E2%80%99s%20equipment%20being%20repeatedly%20used%2C%20affecting%20617%20individuals%20who%20were%20rendered%20homeless%20or%20deprived%20of%20their%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP-ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20reported%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpunitive%20demolitions%E2%80%9D%20at%2056%2C%20the%20reports%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20demolitions%2C%20often%20enacted%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20removing%20illegal%20construction%2C%20violated%20due%20process%20outlined%20in%20domestic%20and%20international%20human%20rights%20law.%20They%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Muslim-concentrated%20localities%20were%20targeted%2C%20while%20Muslim-owned%20properties%20were%20selectively%20demolished%2C%20leaving%20nearby%20Hindu-owned%20properties%20untouched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20not%20the%20only%20vehicles%20used%2C%20JCB%20bulldozers%20have%20become%20the%20brand%20of%20choice%2C%20with%20the%20company%20earning%20nicknames%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Jihadi%20Control%20Board%E2%80%99%20from%20right-wing%20media%20and%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20International%20had%20earlier%20written%20to%20JCB%20regarding%20the%20matter.%20In%20response%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20they%20had%20no%20control%20or%20responsibility%20over%20how%20its%20products%20are%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20Guiding%20Principles%20on%20Business%20and%20Human%20Rights%2C%20JCB%20has%20a%20responsibility%20to%20respect%20human%20rights%20and%20conduct%20due%20diligence%20to%20identify%2C%20prevent%2C%20and%20mitigate%20adverse%20human%20rights%20impacts%20linked%20to%20its%20operations%2C%20the%20human%20rights%20group%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20international%20standards%2C%20JCB%20is%20responsible%20for%20addressing%20what%20third-party%20buyers%20do%20with%20its%20equipment.%20The%20company%20must%20stop%20looking%20away%20as%20JCB%20machines%20are%20used%20to%20target%20and%20punish%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20while%20people%20sloganeer%20anti-Muslim%20vitriol%20mounted%20from%20atop%20these%20bulldozers.%20JCB%20cannot%20continue%20to%20evade%20responsibility%20while%20its%20machines%20are%20repeatedly%20used%20to%20inflict%20human%20rights%20abuses%2C%E2%80%9D%20Callamard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707314020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslims-targeted-in-128-demolitions-617-people-affected-amnesty-reports-on-bulldozer-action%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP-ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20reported%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpunitive%20demolitions%E2%80%9D%20at%2056%2C%20the%20report%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslims-targeted-in-128-demolitions-617-people-affected-amnesty-reports-on-bulldozer-action%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Rishi%20K