strong%3EGates%20closed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20territory%20administration%20also%20prevented%20the%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20from%20addressing%20a%20party%20rally%20in%20the%20region%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20said%20Imran%20Nabi%20Dar%2C%20a%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20was%20scheduled%20to%20address%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20the%20Sunderbani%20area%20of%20Poonch%20where%20a%20crowd%20of%20about%203000%20party%20workers%20and%20local%20leaders%20had%20gathered%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20party%20source%20said%20that%20both%20the%20main%20gate%20and%20a%20controlled-access%20passage%20to%20Dr%20Farooq%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20residence%20Bhatindi%20locality%20of%20Jammu%2C%20from%20where%20Omar%20was%20scheduled%20to%20leave%20for%20Poonch%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20were%20locked%20from%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20said%20that%20many%20party%20workers%20and%20leaders%20who%20had%20gathered%20at%20Sunderbani%20were%20disappointed%20as%20the%20National%20Conference%20vice-president%20could%20not%20reach%20the%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPreventing%20political%20parties%20from%20reaching%20out%20to%20their%20workers%20is%20an%20undemocratic%20act%20and%20our%20party%20condemns%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20behaviour%2C%E2%80%9D%20NC%20spokesperson%20Dar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20gave%20approval%20to%20the%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%202023%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20which%20has%20included%20the%20Pahari-speaking%20people%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20list%2C%20sporadic%20protests%20broke%20out%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20Union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20said%20that%20a%20minor%20protest%20broke%20out%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Jammu%20after%20the%20bill%20got%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20nod%20through%20voice%20vote%20on%20Tuesday.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20tribal%20students%20raised%20slogans%20against%20the%20bill%20and%20tried%20to%20take%20out%20a%20protest%20from%20the%20university%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zahid%20Parwaz%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20tribal%20leader..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoudhary%2C%20who%20is%20the%20state%20president%20of%20Gujjar%20Bakkerwal%20Youth%20Welfare%20Conference%2C%20a%20non-profit%20which%20champions%20the%20cause%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20population%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20authorities%20have%20prevented%20students%20and%20other%20tribals%20from%20raising%20their%20voice%20against%20the%20reservation%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecurity%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20at%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20main%20gate%20to%20prevent%20the%20students%20from%20exercising%20their%20democratic%20rights.%20Some%20of%20us%20were%20detained%20at%20Kothi%20Bagh%20police%20station%20(in%20Srinagar)%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon%2C%E2%80%9D%20Choudhary%2C%20who%20also%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20the%20purported%20security%20built-up%20outside%20the%20university%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%20in%20charge%20of%20Jammu%20University%2C%20Professor%20Anju%20Bhasin%2C%20said%20that%20she%20also%20noticed%20the%20security%20forces%20outside%20the%20university%20gate%20when%20she%20came%20to%20her%20office%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20UT%20administration%20may%20have%20done%20it%20to%20preempt%20any%20disturbance.%20Our%20university%20has%20no%20role%20in%20matters%20outside%20the%20campus%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%20amends%20the%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%2C%201989%20to%20create%20separate%20lists%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20for%20Union%20Territories%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20adds%20four%20communities%20to%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20including%20Gadda%20Brahmin%2C%20Koli%2C%20Paddari%20Tribe%2C%20and%20Pahari%20Ethnic%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lower%20house%20also%20passed%20the%20Constitution%20(Scheduled%20Castes)%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20adds%20Valmiki%20community%20as%20a%20synonym%20of%20Chura%2C%20Balmiki%2C%20Bhangi%2C%20and%20Mehtar%20communities%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Rights%20of%20tribals%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20group%20of%20lawyers%20staged%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20bill%20in%20Panama%20Chowk%20locality%20of%20Jammu%20on%20Tuesday.%20A%20video%20from%20the%20protest%20shows%20some%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20personnel%20bundling%20three%20lawyers%20into%20the%20back%20of%20one%20of%20their%20vehicles%20who%20raised%20slogans%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGujjar%20and%20Bakkerwals%20make%20up%20the%20third%20largest%20population%20(of%20J%26amp%3BK)%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20lawyer%20is%20heard%20screaming%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20hit%20the%20streets%20and%20fight%20for%20our%20rights.%20We%20are%20not%20afraid%20of%20their%20tyranny.%20We%20have%20fought%20against%20militancy%20in%20the%20border%20areas.%20We%20have%20kept%20the%20flag%20of%20India%20flying%20high%20but%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20any%20fiddling%20with%20the%20rights%20of%20tribals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinor%20protests%20against%20the%20controversial%20bill%20were%20also%20reported%20from%20the%20summer%20capital%20Srinagar%2C%20and%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shopian%2C%20Pulwama%20and%20Kulgam%20districts%20that%20serve%20as%20the%20temporary%20home%20for%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20who%20traverse%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20during%20the%20summer%20months%20along%20with%20their%20families%20and%20livestock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20groups%20have%20been%20up%20in%20arms%20against%20the%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20of%20granting%20tribal%20status%20to%20the%20culturally-moored%20and%20economically%20privileged%20Paharis%2C%20arguing%20that%20they%20will%20nibble%20away%20at%20the%20jobs%20and%20other%20opportunities%20reserved%20for%20their%20poor%20and%20downtrodden%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVote%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20however%20denied%20the%20charge%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20bill%20was%20one%20of%20the%20several%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cempower%20the%20backward%20and%20downtrodden%E2%80%9D%20sections%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20after%20its%20special%20status%20was%20read%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20NC%E2%80%99s%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%2C%20had%20demanded%20that%20the%20union%20government%20should%20guarantee%20that%20the%20quota%20for%20existing%20STs%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20protected%20following%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20new%20reservation%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20political%20experts%2C%20the%20bill%20is%20part%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20turn%20the%20socially-fragmented%20population%20of%20Paharis%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20into%20a%20political%20vote%20bank%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20has%20struggled%20to%20make%20inroads%20in%20the%20Muslim-majority%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20been%20wooing%20the%2012%20lakh%20Pahari-speaking%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20who%20can%20influence%20the%20outcome%20of%20assembly%20elections%20in%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20constituencies%20since%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202022%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20told%20a%20packed%20crowd%20in%20Rajouri%20town%20that%20the%20Pahari%20community%20was%20going%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20announcement%20came%20after%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reorganisation%20Act%202019%20provided%20reservation%20for%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20assembly%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707308004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07173820%2F738c0fdb-2245-4405-b5d0-80734653847e.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-tribal-paharis-protest-internet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20territory%20administration%20also%20suspended%20internet%20in%20two%20districts%20of%20Pir%20Panjal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-tribal-paharis-protest-internet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20has%20former%20Fox%20News%20host%20Tucker%20Carlson%20said%20on%20Putin%2C%20the%20war%20and%20Ukraine%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707307380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-tucker-carlson-fox-news_6446884.jpg%3F20240206221743%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-has-former-fox-news-host-tucker-carlson-said-on-putin-the-war-and-ukraine-13066018%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Controversial%20right-wing%20US%20journalist%20Tucker%20Carlson%20will%20shortly%20release%20an%20interview%20he%20conducted%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-has-former-fox-news-host-tucker-carlson-said-on-putin-the-war-and-ukraine-13066018%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhat-has-former-fox-news-host-tucker-carlson-said-on-putin-the-war-and-ukraine-13066018%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhat-has-former-fox-news-host-tucker-carlson-said-on-putin-the-war-and-ukraine-13066018%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bleak%20Urban%20Outlay%2C%20Neglected%20Himalayan%20States%3A%20Decoding%20the%202024%20Budget's%20Election%20Rhetoric%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F28151132%2FBudget-136445-pixahive.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20launched%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-elusive-smartness-in-indias-smart-cities%5C%22%3ESmart%20Cities%20Mission%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20envisioned%20as%20the%20lighthouse%20of%20city%20development.%20With%20a%20total%20of%20100%20cities%20included%20in%20its%20proposal%2C%20this%20flagship%20programme%20received%20budgetary%20support%20and%20continued%20to%20dominate%20urban%20planning%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20urban%20planning%20or%20cities%20in%20the%20Union%20budget%20speech.%20It%20appears%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20smart%20cities%20has%20faded%2C%20with%20only%20a%20passing%20reference%20to%20urbanisation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fhalf-of-countrys-population-will-be-living-in-cities-in-few-decades-union-minister-kaushal-kishore%2Farticleshow%2F106023424.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Etaking%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20the%20interim%20budget%20boasted%20of%20its%20revenue%20receipts%2C%20saying%20that%20there%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbudget%2Fbudget_parliament%2F2024%2FInterim_Union_Budget_Analysis-2024-25.pdf%5C%22%3Eincrease%20of%2011%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024-25.%20However%2C%20the%20growth%20in%20revenue%20receipts%20is%20driven%20by%20corporate%20tax%20and%20income%20tax%2C%20which%20is%20estimated%20to%20grow%20by%2013%25%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20between%202018-19%20and%202022-23%2C%20individual%20tax%20collections%20in%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fk-shape-widens-govt-personal-income-tax-collection-corporate-tax%5C%22%3Ehave%20surged%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20a%20whopping%2076%25.%20However%2C%20the%20corporate%20sector%20share%20in%20that%20tax%20collected%20has%20inched%20by%20only%20a%20fraction%2C%20just%2024.45%25%2C%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20implies%20that%20common%20people%20and%20the%20poor%20are%20contributing%20more%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20development.%20However%2C%20the%20dividends%20seem%20to%20be%20favouring%20corporates%2C%20as%20their%20tax%20percentage%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2F2022%2FAug%2F14%2Fin-first-two-years-of-corporate-tax-cut-govt-suffers-rs-184-lakh-crore-loss-2487445.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20reduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%2030%25%20to%2020%25%2C%20and%20even%2015%25%20in%20some%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20looks%20at%20the%20expenditure%20part%2C%20Budget%202024-25%20is%20a%20sheer%20disaster.%20The%20social%20welfare%20expenditure%20has%20been%20reduced%20from%20the%20budgetary%20estimates%20of%202023-24%2C%20from%20Rs%202.42%20lakh%20crore%20to%20Rs%202.25%20lakh%20crore%20in%20revenue%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fgovernment-schemes-where-are-we-on-urban-agenda%5C%22%3EGovernment%20Schemes%3A%20Where%20Are%20We%20on%20Urban%20Agenda%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBudgetary%20allocation%20for%20urban%20areas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20urban%20domain%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20more%20pathetic.%20The%20total%20outlay%20falls%20far%20below%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20budgetary%20allocation%20for%20urban%20areas%20in%20the%20year%202023-24%20was%20Rs%2076%2C431%20crore.%20However%2C%20the%20revised%20estimate%20is%20approximately%20Rs%2069%2C270%20crore%2C%20indicating%20a%20shortfall%20of%20Rs%207%2C000%20crore.%20This%20shortfall%20should%20have%20been%20accommodated%20in%20the%20succeeding%20year%20of%202024-25.%20However%2C%20the%20total%20proposal%20for%202024-25%20stands%20at%20Rs%2077%2C525%20crore%2C%20just%201%25%20more%20than%20the%20previous%20year.%20Considering%20inflation%20and%20other%20factors%2C%20this%20suggests%20a%20decline%20in%20real%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20also%20find%20out%20where%20the%20shortfall%20has%20been%20in%20both%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2Fdoc%2Feb%2Fvol1.pdf%5C%22%3Erevised%20budget%20estimates%20and%20the%20proposal%20for%202024-25.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20massive%20shortfall%20of%20nearly%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore%20from%20the%20budgetary%20proposals%20and%20revised%20estimates%20of%202023-24.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20shortfall%20of%20around%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20in%20these%20schemes%20since%20last%20year.%20The%20figures%20are%20as%3A%20the%20proposal%20was%20Rs%2046%2C103%20crore%2C%20whereas%20the%20revised%20estimate%20is%20Rs%2038%2C396%20crore%20and%20the%20proposed%20outlay%20for%202024-25%20is%20Rs%2044%2C545%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%20schemes%2C%20it%20is%20interesting%20that%20around%20Rs%2019%2C518%20crore%20was%20allocated%20for%20metro%20rail%20projects%2C%20as%20per%20budget%20estimates%20of%202023-24%2C%20and%20in%20the%20current%20proposal%20of%202024-25%2C%20it%20stands%20at%20Rs%2021%2C335%20crore.%20That%20means%2048%25%20of%20the%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20(in%20the%20urban%20category)%20will%20be%20usurped%20by%20the%20capital%20intensive%20metro%20projects%2C%20whereas%20the%20demand%20was%20for%20more%20buses%20in%20the%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20notable%20feature%20is%20a%20major%20setback%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20capital%20assets%20or%20urban%20infrastructure.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20drastic%20fall%20of%20around%20Rs%208%2C000%20crore%2C%20from%20Rs%2041%2C830%20crore%20as%20proposed%20in%20the%202023-24%20outlay%20to%20Rs%2033%2C779%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20outlay%20for%202024-25%20also%20remains%20lesser%20than%20the%20previous%20year%20at%20Rs%2039%2C861%20crore.%20Now%2C%20where%20is%20it%20that%20the%20budget%20could%20not%20be%20spent%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20the%20major%20fall%20has%20been%20in%20almost%20all%20the%20flagship%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outlay%20in%20the%20Smart%20Cities%E2%80%99%20proposal%20fell%20from%20Rs%207%2C634%20crore%20to%20Rs%207%2C535%20crore%20in%20the%20revised%20budget%20of%202023-24%2C%20with%20a%20major%20slash%20in%20the%202024-25%20outlay%20to%20Rs%202%2C236%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20for%20AMRUT%2C%20the%20proposal%20sees%20a%20Rs%205%2C000%20cut%20from%20Rs%207%2C634%20crore%20to%20Rs%202%2C236%20crore%3B%20PMAY(U)%2C%20the%20housing%20trumpet%20being%20blown%20by%20the%20finance%20minister%2C%20also%20does%20not%20match%20the%20noise.%20The%20total%20outlay%20in%202023-24%20was%20Rs%2022%2C967%20crore%2C%20whereas%20the%20revised%20estimate%20is%20at%20Rs%2019%2C966%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20a%20shortfall%20of%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20proposal%20for%202024-25%20is%20Rs%2023%2C920%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20just%201%25%20higher%20than%20the%20previous%20year%E2%80%99s%20proposal.%20Considering%20inflation%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20construction%2C%20there%20is%20a%20downslide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%2C%20which%20started%20in%20rocket%20mode%2C%20also%20fell%20from%20expectations.%20Against%20the%20total%20outlay%20of%20Rs%204%2C238%20crore%2C%20the%20revised%20estimate%20for%202023-24%20is%20at%20Rs%201%2C978%20crore%2C%20a%20fall%20of%20nearly%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%2C%20and%20a%20proposed%20figure%20of%20Rs%204%2C246%20crore%2C%20once%20again%20not%20even%20matching%20the%20previous%20year%E2%80%99s%20budgetary%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funpaid-work-discouraged-workers-essential-services-as-gifts-jayati-ghosh-on-modi-govts-policies%5C%22%3EUnpaid%20Work%2C%20Discouraged%20Workers%2C%20Essential%20Services%20as%20%E2%80%98Gifts%E2%80%99%3A%20Jayati%20Ghosh%20on%20Modi%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Policies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPromises%20versus%20reality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20minister%20used%20the%20terms%20%E2%80%9Chousing%2C%20water%2C%20sanitation%2C%20and%20finance%20for%20all%E2%80%9D%20in%20her%20remarks.%20But%20how%20does%20these%20items%20fare%20in%20the%20current%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20despite%20its%2010-year%20rule%20and%20promises%20of%20providing%20houses%20to%20everyone%20within%20the%20first%20five-year%20period%20from%202014%20to%202019%2C%20admits%20that%20there%20is%20still%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbudget%2Fbudget-2024-new-housing-scheme-for-middle-class-to-propel-development-of-real-estate-3382092%2F%5C%22%3Eshortfall%20of%20nearly%2020%20million%20houses%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20rural%20areas.%20The%20urban%20figures%20have%20not%20been%20mentioned%2C%20but%20various%20estimates%20suggest%20that%20the%20figure%20is%20more%20than%20three%20million.%20How%20will%20this%20be%20addressed%3F%20As%20seen%20above%2C%20the%20figures%20belie%20the%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20water%20supply%20and%20sanitation%20category%2C%20the%20figures%20remain%20static%20at%20Rs%2064%2C000%20crore%20under%20the%20revenue%20expenditure%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeglecting%20the%20Himalayan%20states%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20notable%20feature%20of%20the%20current%20budgetary%20proposal%20is%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20states.%20These%2013%20states%20have%20been%20demanding%20special%20financial%20packages%20and%20architecture%20owing%20to%20their%20extreme%20vulnerabilities%2C%20both%20climatic%20and%20geographic.%20It%20was%20expected%20that%20the%20government%20would%20assist%20these%20states%20in%20promoting%20tourism%20and%20allied%20sectors%2C%20such%20as%20fruit%20processing%20plants%2C%20agri-based%20allied%20help%20in%20the%20forms%20of%20procurement%2C%20and%20compressed%20atmosphere%20stores%2C%20which%20are%20capital-intensive%20technologies%20ensuring%20them%20a%20better%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20linking%20their%20development%20models%20to%20climate%20change%20realities%20was%20anticipated.%20However%2C%20nothing%20has%20been%20said%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reduction%20in%20apple%20import%20duty%20is%20negatively%20impacting%20farmers%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%20the%20three%20major%20apple-producing%20states.%20Fruit%20processing%20plants%20were%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20to%20mitigate%20the%20current%20challenges.%20However%2C%20the%20Himalayan%20mountains%20remain%20far%20beyond%20the%20domain%20of%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20financial%20assistance%20ambit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20budget%20resembles%20more%20of%20an%20election%20speech%2C%20eulogising%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20rather%20than%20addressing%20the%20essentialities%20of%20the%20current%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETikender%20Singh%20Panwar%20was%20once%20directly%20elected%20deputy%20mayor%20of%20Shimla.%20He%20was%20linked%20with%20the%20Leh%20Vision%20document%20and%20has%20written%20vision%20documents%20for%20a%20dozen%20cities.%20Author%20of%20two%20books%2C%20he%20is%20an%20urban%20specialist%20working%20in%20the%20design%20of%20inclusive%20cities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707307236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F28151132%2FBudget-136445-pixahive.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fbleak-urban-outlay-neglected-himalayan-states-decoding-the-2024-budgets-election-rhetoric%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%2C%20there's%20a%20massive%20shortfall%20of%20nearly%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore%20from%20the%20budgetary%20proposals%20and%20revised%20estimates%20of%202023-24.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fbleak-urban-outlay-neglected-himalayan-states-decoding-the-2024-budgets-election-rhetoric%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Israel%20ties%20without%20recognition%20of%20Palestinian%20state%3A%20Saudi%20Arabia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707306731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107493626%2Cimgsize-481700.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fno-israel-ties-without-recognition-of-palestinian-state-saudi-arabia%2Farticleshow%2F107493394.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107493394.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20has%20informed%20the%20United%20States%20that%20it%20would%20not%20establish%20diplomatic%20ties%20with%20Israel%20until%20an%20independent%20Palestinian%20state%20is%20established%20on%201967%20lines%2C%20with