0without%20Kambli's%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20plan%2C%20Anjali%20was%20joined%20by%20Kambli%20in%20the%20city%20and%20they%20checked%20in%20at%20the%20hotel%20together%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Rakesh%20arrived%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20meeting%2C%20Rakesh's%20arrival%20enraged%20Kambli%20and%20a%20fight%20erupted%20between%20the%20two.%20The%20fight%20left%20Kambli%20injured%2C%20seeing%20which%20the%20couple%20fled.%20They%20also%20took%20away%20two%20mobile%20phones%20belonging%20to%20Kambli%20-%20which%20allegedly%20had%20their%20intimate%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20phone%20call%20from%20Rakesh%20later%20in%20the%20day%20alerted%20the%20hotel%20authorities%20and%20they%20informed%20the%20Guwahati%20city%20police.%20The%20cops%20promptly%20went%20through%20the%20hotel%20register%2C%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20and%20airport%20passengers'%20list%20to%20zero%20in%20on%20the%20two%20suspects.%20Anjali%20and%20Rakesh%20were%20arrested%20near%20the%20hotel%20before%20they%20could%20board%20the%209%3A15%20pm%20flight%20to%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20remains%20under%20investigation%20as%20the%20cops%20are%20trying%20to%20piece%20together%20the%20events%20that%20led%20to%20their%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707206400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Frjidfu38_guwahati-airport_625x300_20_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fguwahati-news%2Flove-triangle-ends-in-guwahati-murder-over-intimate-pics-solved-in-hours-5004009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20love%20triangle%20ended%20in%20a%20brutal%20murder%20at%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20in%20Guwahati%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20was%20solved%20swiftly%20before%20the%20accused%20could%20fly%20half%20a%20thousand%20kilometres%20away%20to%20Kolkata.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fguwahati-news%2Flove-triangle-e