20by%20%26quot%3Bcoercion%2C%20fraud%2C%20or%20misrepresentation%20(with%20regard%20to%20identity)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20told%20NDTV%20a%20website%20is%20being%20prepped%20to%20accept%20details%20of%20live-in%20relationship%2C%20which%20will%20be%20verified%20with%20the%20District%20Registrar%2C%20who%20will%20conduct%20a%20%26quot%3Bsummary%20inquiry%26quot%3B%20to%20establish%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20relationship.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20he%20may%20summon%20either%20or%20both%20partners%2C%20or%20anybody%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20registration%20be%20refused%2C%20the%20Registrar%20must%20inform%20in%20writing%20his%2Fher%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Btermination%26quot%3B%20of%20registered%20live-in%20relationships%20requires%20a%20written%20statement%2C%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bprescribed%20format%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20invite%20police%20investigation%20if%20the%20Registrar%20feels%20reasons%20for%20the%20relationship%20ending%20are%20%26quot%3Bincorrect%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%26quot%3B.%20Parents%20or%20guardians%20of%20those%20under%2021%20will%20also%20be%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFailure%20to%20submit%20live-in%20relationship%20declarations%2C%20or%20providing%20false%20information%2C%20could%20land%20one%20in%20jail%20for%20three%20months%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%20Anyone%20who%20fails%20to%20register%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20will%20face%20a%20maximum%20of%20six%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20be%20fined%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%20Even%20a%20delay%20in%20registration%2C%20by%20as%20little%20as%20a%20month%2C%20will%20trigger%20a%20jail%20term%20of%20up%20to%20three%20months%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20key%20points%20in%20the%20section%20on%20live-in%20relationships%20in%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20that%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Assembly%20Tuesday%20morning%20are%20that