Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20boxes%20they%20usually%20feature%20designs%20like%20a%20cow%2C%20milk%2C%20etc.%20The%20imagery%20is%20not%20exciting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20brands%20that%20focus%20on%20good%20packaging%20do%20not%20tell%20a%20story%20through%20it.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20voice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20pain%20point%20was%20that%20of%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20tough%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Emithais%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20rival%20that%20in%20other%20cities.%20This%20is%20because%2C%20for%20quality%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20quality%20raw%20materials%20are%20needed.%20These%20are%20expensive.%20If%20employed%2C%20this%20would%20in%20turn%20increase%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20So%2C%20most%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20makers%20resort%20to%20ingredients%20that%20can%20help%20them%20achieve%20a%20balance%20between%20cost-effectiveness%20and%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPistabarfi%20is%20built%20on%20addressing%20these%20points.%20The%20brothers%20emphasise%20that%20the%20idea%20behind%20the%20venture%20has%20always%20been%20to%20stick%20to%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F248039%2Frida-sajad-noida-woman-entrepreneur-shireen-e-yemberzal-mithai-wagon-food-startup-small-business-dry-fruit-sweets-no-sugar-no-preservatives-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20roots%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20play%20to%20their%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20793px)%20100vw%2C%20793px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F2-1706615039.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22793%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Janta%20Dairy%20outlet%20at%20Elphinstone%20Road%20in%20Mumbai%20is%20a%20haunt%20for%20the%20locals%20who%20come%20