0chores.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20she%20adopted%20better%20technology%20and%20scientific%20farming%20methods%20to%20improve%20the%20yield%20and%20quality%20of%20millet%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20with%20Kamala%E2%80%99s%20help%2C%20she%20associated%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F81135%2Fchennai-designer-adaptive-clothing-for-the-disabled%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChennai-based%20non-profit%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20MS%20Swaminathan%20Research%20Foundation%20(MSSRF)%2C%20where%20she%20learned%20the%20skill%20of%20modern%20conservation%2C%20helping%20more%20women%20gain%20employment%20in%20rural%20areas.%20She%20has%20trained%20around%202%2C500%20farmers%20in%20millet%20farming%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Raimati%2C%20millet%20cultivation%20transformed%20her%20life.%20She%20now%20leads%20a%20self-help%20group%20of%20women%20farmers%20and%20farmer%20producer%20companies%20to%20process%20millets%20into%20value-added%20products%20like%20%3Cem%3Epakoras%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eladdus%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20sell%20at%20the%20local%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20she%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20establishing%20a%20farm%20school%20in%20her%20village%20by%20donating%20her%20ancestral%20family%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20she%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20her%20active%20participation%20in%20revitalising%20traditional%20rice%20and%20millet%20varieties%20at%20the%202023%20G20%20Summit%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20for%20which%20she%20was%20personally%20appreciated%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20Draupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20national-level%20recognition%20has%20not%20only%20brought%20me%20immense%20respect%20from%20my%20in-laws%20but%20also%20from%20global%20leaders.%20It%20motivates%20me%20to%20conserve%20more%20varieties%20and%20make%20my%20state%20proud%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Raimati.%3